<firstl><l ln="1        ">&indent;The young women</l></firstl>
<l ln="2        ">Do not wear flowers</l>
<l ln="3        ">In their hair</l>
<l ln="4        ">During the spring</l>
<l ln="5        ">And summer</l>
<l ln="6        ">Solstices</l>
<l ln="7        ">&indent;&indent;But all year round</l>
<l ln="8        ">They spit</l>
<l ln="9        ">&indent;&indent;&indent;With great precision</l>
